title: Ruth Finley and the Fashion Calendar, an interview with Natalie Nudell
itunes:title: Ruth Finley and the Fashion Calendar, an interview with Natalie Nudell
description:
A tribute to the passing of American fashion insider, Ruth Finley, whose Fashion Calendar was and continues to be a critical element in producing Fashion Week.
